<div class="card" role="region" aria-label="Newsletter sign-up">

  <span class="eyebrow">Free newsletter</span>

  <h2>AI tools that <em>actually work</em>.</h2>
  <p class="sub-copy">
    Weekly breakdowns of the best AI tools, prompts &amp; workflows —
    straight to your inbox. No fluff.
  </p>

  <div class="input-row">
    <input
      type="email"
      id="bh-email"
